description:
Appoint a supplier to provide mobile voice and data services to the Council. The project deliverables for this contract are as follows:

&bull;	Appoint a single service provider;
&bull;	Provide continual monitoring of contract charges/tariffs, in order to obtain value for money;
&bull;	Provide a single bill facility;
&bull;	Provide migration of service from existing network operator to alternative (if required);
&bull;	Provide a choice of mobile phone and tablet devices, offering value-for-money solutions; and
&bull;	Provide the flexibility to increase/decrease data and voice usage without incurring excessive additional charges.

